advancements.youkaishomecoming.advanceme: Brew and drink an alcoholic drink and obtain Drunk effect
Plant Coffea on Podzol, Mud, or Soul Soil
Have a crab grab your water bucket when attempting to bucket a crab
Let cucumber climb ropes and harvest the top cucumber of a 3-block tall cucumber crop
Steam a plate meal or bamboo meal. Note that they heavily obstruct steam.
Feed Reimu all appealing food from Youkai's Homecoming to make her happy and give you her hairband
Make Rainbow Roll Slice and Volcano Roll Slice
Cut the leaves off a mature grape crop so that it can grow larger. Make sure it has 3 ropes in a row to climb onto.
Harvest grape hanging under a grape branch
Get a Sweet Ormosia Mochi Mixed Boiled
Obtain Koishi's Hat after playing with Koishi
When Rumia takes more than 40 damage, she will convert to Ex. Rumia. Defeat Ex. Rumia with danmaku and obtain Rumia's Hairband.
Receives a phone call from Koishi in the nether in Youkaifying effect
Steam an item on the 18th rack
Eat a bowl of flesh feast
Drink until you have maximum Drunk effect
Use small iron pot to take a serve of food from short pot / stockpot
Plant Red Bean on Coarse Dirt, Mud, or Clay
When you eat flesh in front of villagers, Reimu will try to exterminate you. Defat Reimu and obtain her spellcard
Jump in the basin to squeeze juice out of grapes
Make Otoro Nigiri, Lorelei Nigiri, Tobiko Gunkan, and Rainbow Futomaki Slice
Obtain Suwako's Hat after collecting enough faith
In youkaified or youkaifying effect, give the straw hat to a frog
Collect tea leaves before tea crop starts flowering
Drink all kinds of tea in original flavor
In youkaified effect, trade with Rumia to get Danmaku
Plants an Udumbara with its leaves. It grows under moonlight and shrinks under sunlight.
Get an Udubara flower. It will only appear for 10 seconds during full moon.
Harvest Udumbara Leaves from Udumbaar crop near maturity
block.youkaishomecoming.fine_grid_framed: Fine Grid Framed Sikkui Trap Door
block.youkaishomecoming.light_blue_red_v: Light Blue Red Velvet Candle Cake
block.youkaishomecoming.light_gray_red_v: Light Gray Red Velvet Candle Cake
effect.youkaishomecoming.confident.descr: Increase invulnerability time after being attacked
effect.youkaishomecoming.drunk.descripti: Increase attack damage, but you feel drunk. You can't have sobering drink while having this effect. Drunk effect can stack up to 5 layers.
effect.youkaishomecoming.earthy.descript: Digest and heal when player is full
effect.youkaishomecoming.fairy.descripti: Reduce max HP and melee attack damage. Gives speed and healing boost. Enables danmaku. Reduce player hitbox for Danmaku
effect.youkaishomecoming.higi.descriptio: Boost attack damage and movement speed, heal slowly
effect.youkaishomecoming.mature.descript: Consume Nourishment effect duration to reduce incoming damage
effect.youkaishomecoming.meditation.desc: Gain experience gradually when not moving
effect.youkaishomecoming.phantom.descrip: Prevents vibration from you and your projectiles. Warps you to the top of the world when falling into the void. Heals every 3 seconds under moonlight. Reduced damage taken when under full moon.
effect.youkaishomecoming.refreshing.desc: Immune to fire, puts down fire
effect.youkaishomecoming.sober.descripti: Prevents phantom spawn, nausea, youkaization, and sleep. You can't have another alcohol or sobering drink while having this effect.
effect.youkaishomecoming.tea_polyphenols: Boost attack speed, heal every 3 seconds when under sunlight
effect.youkaishomecoming.unconscious.des: You won't be targeted by mobs. Terminates when you attack or open loot chests.

youkaishomecoming.flask.info_drink: Stores 4 bottles of drink. Consume 0.2 bottles per slip
youkaishomecoming.flask.info_sauce: Stores 4 bottles of sauce. Consume 0.2 bottles per use on Pots and Cuisine Table
youkaishomecoming.no_consume_2: Allows using %s and %s danmaku without consumption.
youkaishomecoming.obtain_blood: Kill human mobs with knife and have glass bottle in off hand while in %s or %s effect
youkaishomecoming.obtain_fairy_ice: Rarely dropped when you got hit by Cirno's Danmaku while wearing full leather suits. Dropped from Cirno. Could be obtained by trading with Cirno as well.
youkaishomecoming.obtain_flesh: Kill human mobs with knife while in %s or %s effect
youkaishomecoming.obtain_frozen_frog: Dropped when Cirno freezes a frog. Rarely dropped from Cirno when defeated with Danmaku.
youkaishomecoming.obtain_koishi_hat: Drops when blocking Koishi attacks %s times in a row
youkaishomecoming.obtain_reimu_hairband: Feed Reimu a variety of food
youkaishomecoming.obtain_rumia_hairband: Drops when player defeat Ex. Rumia with Danmaku
youkaishomecoming.obtain_suwako_hat: Drops when frog with hat eats %s different kinds of raiders in front of villagers
youkaishomecoming.reimu_flesh: Reimu: You shall not eat it. Last warning.
youkaishomecoming.reimu_warn: Reimu: Drink some tea and keep your sanity. Last warning.
youkaishomecoming.steamer.no_cap: Cap top rack to steam faster
youkaishomecoming.steamer.no_heat: Next Step: Put heat source beneath
youkaishomecoming.tooltip.drying_rack: Only works directly under the sun
youkaishomecoming.tooltip.kettle: Right click with water bucket or water bottle to fill water
youkaishomecoming.tooltip.moon_lantern_h: When holding in hand, Udumbara effect will always trigger at night regardless if player can see full moons
youkaishomecoming.tooltip.moon_lantern_p: Udumbara within 3x3x3 blocks below this latern will grow as night as if they can see full moon.
youkaishomecoming.tooltip.spell_target: Requires targeting an entity to activate
youkaishomecoming.usage_cirno_hairband: Your magic damage freezes target (and frogs).
youkaishomecoming.usage_danmaku: While in %s or %s effect, or equip touhou hats, you can shoot danmaku
youkaishomecoming.usage_fairy_ice: Throw to deal damage and freeze target.
youkaishomecoming.usage_fairy_wings: When you have %s, enables creative flight.
youkaishomecoming.usage_frozen_frog: Throw toward target to summon a frog.
youkaishomecoming.usage_reimu_hairband: Enables creative flight. Your danmaku damage bypasses magical protection.
youkaishomecoming.usage_rumia_hairband: Drops heads when killing mobs. Flesh and blood drops no longer require knife (bonus when still using knife).
youkaishomecoming.usage_straw_hat: While in %s or %s effect, you can equip it on frogs to allow them to eat raiders
